sources.title: MODEL A FORD INTRODUCTORY FILM
sources.description: This originally silent film marked the introduction of the all new 1928 Model A. 23 minutes in length. This film shows many inner workings of the car and includes scenes of various road tests. A musical soundtrack has been added. All music in this presentation comes from the public domain. Please visit www.orlandomodelas.com for more information about the Model A.
